fields.headline: Green Flowers
fields.contents: Found them? In Mercia?! The coconut's tropical! The swallow may fly south with the sun.

fields.headline: Blue Flowers
fields.contents: Help, help, I'm being repressed! You don't frighten us, English pig-dogs! Go and boil your bottoms, sons of a silly person!

fields.headline: Inside a Church
fields.contents: Don't be too proud of this technological terror you've constructed. The ability to destroy a planet is insignificant next to the power of the Force.

fields.headline: The Shard
fields.contents: Every time I learn something new, it pushes some old stuff out of my brain.

fields.headline: A Lamp Post
fields.contents: It will not go out of my mind that if we pass this post and lantern either we shall find strange adventures or else some great changes of our fortunes.
